lockquote><br />\n<br />\n有上台？<br />\n點睇gogo司機大佬們既搶單速度？<br />\n<br />\n利：join左gogo 但次次禁左入去唔洗1秒就俾人搶左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739dc65648359108f8c079b0777dac1cc08edccd","tid":20564,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"2.5同3.0turbo係咪差好遠？"},{"pid":"5f55309affd040b80c5679c4fca804bec8c31402","tid":20564,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>棍波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動波 <br />\n雖然棍波係男人浪漫 又慳油啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過搵食車揸棍好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有上台？<br />\n點睇gogo司機大佬們既搶單速度？<br />\n<br />\n利：join左gogo 但次次禁左入去唔洗1秒就俾人搶左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無上台 本身自己有啲包月柯打做<br />\n已經夠供車 不過都有跑下gogo<br />\n啲跑gogo師兄會專買一部電話 就係裝gogo用<br />\n果陣我做gogo開左無幾耐 唔算太多人用<br />\n都接到下柯打 跟住開始多人用 遲1秒接已經無左<br />\n跑gogo真係無得考慮 一睇到就要接"},{"pid":"c382e74ea0c1c0443971ac332349439f181dd8ab","tid":20564,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.5同3.0turbo係咪差好遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未揸過2.5 答你唔到<br />\n我果部係3.0turbo<br />\n不過我覺得應該爭好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打想出車？<br />\n2.5果啲應該歐盟3 只可以揸到19年"},{"pid":"9659a2f43c0395a496254d6fc02b92feb24d07f3","tid":20564,"uid":48502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>棍波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動波 <br />\n雖然棍波係男人浪漫 又慳油啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過搵食車揸棍好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有上台？<br />\n點睇gogo司機大佬們既搶單速度？<br />\n<br />\n利：join左gogo 但次次禁左入去唔洗1秒就俾人搶左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無上台 本身自己有啲包月柯打做<br />\n已經夠供車 不過都有跑下gogo<br />\n啲跑gogo師兄會專買一部電話 就係裝gogo用<br />\n果陣我做gogo開左無幾耐 唔算太多人用<br />\n都接到下柯打 跟住開始多人用 遲1秒接已經無左<br />\n跑gogo真係無得考慮 一睇到就要接</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身都有包月<br />\n只不過平時等貨無野做 join黎試下搵多試少<br />\n點知join 完開機試<br />\n覺得係要完全係要9禁唔理三七廿一先搶到<br />\n最後都係放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4d86dafbab3c257910f54f8b9218a3364ba9ba","tid":20564,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"我本身都有包月<br />\n只不過平時等貨無野做 join黎試下搵多試少<br />\n點知join 完開機試<br />\n覺得係要完全係要9禁唔理三七廿一先搶到<br />\n最後都係放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油呀巴打 做咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔好對gogo太大期望 好難靠佢搵食<br />\n我之前都係得閒先開嚟接<br />\n有時好彩會接到啲返屋企柯打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2291c2337888380ad9b929ac2f4c8e7758274a1","tid":20564,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:18:54.000Z","msg":"我都揸過HIACE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學車果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e886692f48c4b58e0098d303c113f483c9b0af","tid":20564,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都揸過HIACE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學車果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm